OL,6,FCreatively, it was always a little
OL,7,Fawkward having the CBBC presenter link
OL,8,Finto the 5.35pm programme. In those
OL,9,Fdays, the voice behind the globe really
OL,10,Fdid help to establish the authority of
OL,11,Fthe BBC.
OL,13,FBut when the link was simply into The
OL,14,FFlintstones, Cartoon Time or the
OL,15,Fschools quiz First Class it hardly
OL,16,Fmattered in practice.
OL,18,FIt was maybe more of an issue when the
OL,19,F5.35pm programme was not particularly
OL,20,Fchild friendly ` say Masterteam.
OL,3,CThe junction where the CBBC presenter
OL,4,Cwas the BBC One announcer
