OL,6,FBut what about the occasions when a
OL,7,Fsignificant or important programme was
OL,8,Fbeing shown at 5.35pm?
OL,10,FDuring the 1986 Mexico World Cup,
OL,11,FPhillip was allowed to link into the
OL,12,Fregular highlights programme shown
OL,13,Fbetween CBBC and the Six o'Clock News.
OL,15,FOuch.
OL,17,FYou can begin to see why some in
OL,18,FPresentation were apparently less than
OL,19,Fkeen on having someone who wasn't an
OL,20,Fannouncer in the continuity suite.
OL,3,CThe junction where the CBBC presenter
OL,4,Cwas the BBC One announcer
