OL,6,FYou can begin to see why this could
OL,7,Fhave been an issue.
OL,9,FAn announcement before the news by
OL,10,Fsomeone who didn't represent the
OL,11,Fauthority of the BBC, a real handbrake
OL,12,Fturn from the fun in the broom
OL,13,Fcupboard, a voice quite unlike that of
OL,14,Fthe announcers of the time.
OL,16,FSo does anyone know what happened?
OL,18,FA very trivial mystery from a long time
OL,19,Fago needs resolved.
